These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, pony, hedgehog, snake
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, thai, australian, indonesian
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, bus, ship
1. the person driving the airplane is the owner of the snake##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the thai##1
3. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
5. the australian is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the ship is between the indonesian and the owner of the guinea-pig##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Pet         | snake      | guinea-pig | pony | hedgehog |
| Nationality   | australian | pakistani  | thai   | indonesian    |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus    | ship    | boat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola, lemonade, water
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, mexican, polish
4 different games are played: chess, whist, bridge, go
1. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
2. the person drinking water is the mexican##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
4. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
5. the person playing go is on the far left##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the japanese##1
7. the american is between the person drinking water and the person drinking cola##2
8. the polish is between the japanese and the person drinking lemonade##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Beverage         | water | lemonade   | cola | iced-tea  |
| Nationality   | mexican     | american | polish  | japanese |
| Game     | go        | bridge  | whist    | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
City: liverpool, berlin, prague, miami
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, canadian, german
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, folk, dubstep, soul
1. the german is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person traveling to miami##2
2. the argentine is the fan of soul##1
3. the fan of house is the person traveling to prague##1
4. the fan of house is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
5. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4
6. the canadian is between the person traveling to berlin and the american##2
7. the german is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| City          | liverpool | berlin   | miami     | prague     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | german | canadian   | american  |
| Music-Genre     | soul      | folk | dubstep | house |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, apple, peach, grapefruit
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, punk, salsa, soul
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, taxi, boat, jet-ski
1. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
2. the person eating apple is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the fan of soul is the person driving the train##1
6. the person eating peach is the fan of pop##1
7. the fan of salsa is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Food   | broccoli  | grapefruit   | peach     | apple |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | soul      | pop        | punk     |
| Transport         | boat | train | jet-ski | taxi   |

