.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, whist, poker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, swimming, volleyball
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, card-games, video-games, writing
1. the person playing poker is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
7. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
8. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
9. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Game   | mah-jongg   | poker   | whist | canasta |
| Sport         | rugby      | volleyball | golf      | swimming |
| Hobby     | card-games | skydiving        | writing       | video-games  |

