.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, country, dubstep
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, bike, helicopter, train
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the fan of gospel is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is the fan of gospel##1
4. the fan of country is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
6. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
7. the fan of dubstep is in an even position##4
8. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre    | country   | dubstep      | gospel       | electronic |
| Transport   | trike | train | helicopter     | bike |
| Pet     | rat     | guinea-pig  | chinchilla | hamster |

