.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, bellflower, balloon-flower, iris
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, martial-arts, satire, time-travel
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, lavender, coral, turquise
1. the person who likes coral is the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person who likes lavender is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person who likes brown##2
3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
5. the person who growsdaisy is in an even position##4
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is the person who growsdaisy##1
8. the person who likes coral is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Flower      | balloon-flower   | iris          | bellflower | daisy        |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | martial-arts | time-travel   | comedy     |
| Color           | brown | lavender         | turquise         | coral |

