.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, egyptian, american, mexican
House: cottage, cape-cod, futuristic, farmhouse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, disco, electronic, house
1. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
2. the futuristic house is the german##1
3. the farmhouse house is the american##1
4. the american is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of disco is between the cottage house and the german##2
6. the fan of house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
7. the german is in an even position##4
8. the german is between the egyptian and the american##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Nationality         | egyptian | german      | american       | mexican    |
| House           | cape-cod  | futuristic  | farmhouse | cottage |
| Music-Genre   | house      | electronic | disco         | country    |

