.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, water
4 different games are played: go, poker, canasta, backgammon
House: farmhouse, tower, futuristic, wooden
1. the person playing go is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
3. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
4. the tower house is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
6. the wooden house is on the right of the person playing go##1
7. the person playing go is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the person playing poker is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
9. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta         | coffee  | iced-tea     | water         |
| Game        | backgammon | poker | go | canasta         |
| House      | tower         | futuristic  | farmhouse   | wooden |

