.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, light-blue, lavender, coral
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, nigerian, turkish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, thriller, epic, spy
 1. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
 2. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 4. the nigerian is between the person who likes light-blue and the person who likes azure##2
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
 6. the person watching spy movies is the person who likes lavender##1
 7. the turkish is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes azure is in an odd position##4
 9. the malaysian is between the person who likes coral and the person who likes lavender##2
10. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | azure  | lavender    | light-blue | coral    |
| Nationality   | canadian | nigerian | malaysian  | turkish |
| Movie-Genre           | epic   | spy    | adventure        | thriller   |

