.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, motorbike, roller, boat
4 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, chess, poker
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, italian, russian
1. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the russian is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
4. the person playing snooker is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the russian is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
7. the indonesian is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
8. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
9. the person driving the trike is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Transport      | trike                | boat  | motorbike | roller   |
| Game           | poker | snooker | backgammon   | chess |
| Nationality   | indonesian         | dutch     | russian     | italian |

