.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, swimming, sailing, rowing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, musical, romance, western
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, azure, red, brown
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person who likes orange is between the person watching western movies and the person who likes brown##2
6. the person watching romance movies is in an even position##4
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Sport          | sailing    | swimming  | rowing  | cricket |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical | action | romance |
| Color   | red    | orange     | brown    | azure |

