.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, sprite
4 different games are played: poker, chess, scrabble, billiard
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, nurse, analyst, doctor
1. the nurse is between the person drinking fanta and the person playing poker##2
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the analyst##3
4. the doctor is on the left of the person playing chess##1
5. the doctor is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the analyst##3
7. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
8. the person playing scrabble is the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the person playing billiard is between the analyst and the software-developer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | coffee  | sprite    |
| Game   | scrabble   | chess | billiard | poker |
| Job           | doctor      | analyst       | nurse   | software-developer      |

