.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, taxi, skateboard, bike
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, february, january, july
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's birthday is in june##2
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person driving the bike is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person driving the van##2
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
9. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | magic-tricks | dancing  | skydiving  |
| Transport   | skateboard | taxi       | bike | van |
| Birthday         | january   | june      | july | february       |

