.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, cola, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, tram, subway, bus
House: colonial, gothic-revival, victorian, ranch-style
1. the gothic-revival house is in an even position##4
2. the gothic-revival house is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person driving the bus##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is the gothic-revival house##1
7. the colonial house is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the ranch-style house is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | cola      | almond-milk | 7up     | tea    |
| Transport   | bus | skateboard      | tram | subway |
| House           | victorian   | gothic-revival  | colonial     | ranch-style |

