.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, mirinda, tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, dancer, accountant, software-developer
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, magic-tricks, writing
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the electrician is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
4. the dancer is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person drinking milk is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the accountant##2
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is the software-developer##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the electrician is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | mirinda    | milk     | cola    | tea        |
| Job       | accountant   | electrician | dancer | software-developer |
| Hobby   | writing | magic-tricks      | filmmaking    | collecting   |

