3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
5. the social-worker is on the left of the firefighter##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
7. the architect is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
