.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, reading, skydiving
City: new-york, miami, san-francisco, prague
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, june, april, february
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is the person traveling to miami##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person traveling to new-york is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |        4        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | reading   | cooking    | magic-tricks    |
| City           | prague   | miami    | new-york | san-francisco |
| Birthday   | june    | march | april    | february         |

