.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
City: miami, edinburgh, berlin, san-francisco
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, board-games, hiking, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, spy, sports, adventure
1. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
8. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| City    | berlin    | edinburgh    | miami  | san-francisco |
| Hobby   | reading | board-games | baking | hiking      |
| Movie-Genre     | spy   | documentary        | adventure   | sports       |

 